^B@2^Y@3^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|With support for opener's major, responder has a very simple objective -- just deciding whether or not the final contract should be game (4@H or 4@S). If you have 3 or more cards in opener's major suit, that is the suit you should play in, and it is up to you to keep the auction simple and ensure that the final contract is in that suit.|
