2NT is now considered the forcing raise with 4 trumps. I suggest you replace the text file with my new pdf version of the tutorial. BTW, Bergen suggests that you only bid 3N over 1 of a major with 3 card support, 13-15 HCP, and exactly 4-3-3-3 distribution. In other words, it is a very precise and rarely used bid. |
