^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|You are referring to Hand 3 at the top of page 6 of the tutorial. On that hand, the auction goes 1H-P-2H-P, and you hold @Sxxx @HAKJxxx @DAQx @Cx. There are various ways people play to make game tries. I prefer bidding a suit where you have some values, so that partner will place more value on cards in that suit.
