Some people bid suits where they don't have values, and would bid 2S here as the game try. Others bid shortness and would bid 3C as the game try. I think my approach is the simplest, but as long as you and partner agree, the other approaches have their strengths as well. And, regardless of which game try method you use, responder bids 4H to accept the game try, 3H to reject the game try.|
